SLIDING WINDOW USES TWO LEFT AND RIGHT POINTER
- left  → start of window
right → end of window
Sliding Window is a technique used to solve:
Subarray problems
Substring problems
Contiguous sequence problems
Efficiently in O(n) time instead of O(n²).


